261
00:14:00,360 --> 00:14:02,320
that he is quite masochistic.

262
00:14:05,480 --> 00:14:07,480
He and I are impossible.

263
00:14:07,480 --> 00:14:09,480
Impossible.

264
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:13,240
But you

265
