in the following year.

541
00:27:17,560 --> 00:27:19,120
I'm sure I won't feel lost without it.

542
00:27:20,840 --> 00:27:22,480
Mr. Wei, put it on for me.

543
00:27:23,480 --> 00:27:24,240
