571
00:28:36,040 --> 00:28:36,720
She's here.

572
00:28:37,160 --> 00:28:37,680
Where?

573
00:28:37,680 --> 00:28:38,360
Over there.

574
00:28:47,520 --> 00:28:49,280
Long time no see, Penny.

575
00:28:50,120 --> 00:28:51,000
Weilai.

576
00:28:51,480 --> 00:28:52,960
It's been a while.

577
00:28:53,320 --> 00:28:54,440
